    "## Internationalization (i18n)\n",
    "\n",
    "Internationalization bertujuan agar aplikasi dapat secara mudah ditampilkan dalam berbagai jenis bahasa.\n",
    "Secara default, Spring Boot mencari file internationalization pada **src/main/resources**.\n",
    "```\n",
    "src/\n",
    "|--  main/\n",
    "      |-- resources/\n",
    "            |--   messages.properties\n",
    "            |--   messages_de.properties\n",
    "            |--   messages_xx.properties\n",
    "```\n",
    "Format file locale secara default yaitu ```messages.properties``` dan file untul locale yang lainnya adalah ```messages_xx.properties``` dimana ```xx``` menunjukkan kode locale tertentu. \n",
    "\n",
    "Isi dari ```messages.properties``` berupa **key** dan **value** seperti berikut:\n",
    "```txt\n",
    "lang.firstname = First Name\n",
    "lang.lastname = Last Name\n",
    "lang.addstudent = Add Student\n",
    "lang.submit = Submit\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Misal locale yang lainnya adalah locale Bahasa Indonesia, maka isi dari ```messages_in.properties``` berupa **key** dan **value** seperti berikut:\n",
    "```txt\n",
    "lang.firstname = Nama Depan\n",
    "lang.lastname = Nama Belakang\n",
    "lang.addstudent = Tambah Siswa\n",
    "lang.submit = Kirim\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Apabila ada key yang tidak ada pada file locale tertentu, maka nilainya akan menggunakan nilai pada locale default.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Konfigurasi\n",
    "\n",
    "Ada beberapa konfigurasi untuk menggunaka internationalization pada Spring Boot, diantaranya:\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 1. LocaleResolver\n",
    "\n",
    "Bertujuan untuk menentukan locale default yang digunakan pada aplikasi berdasarkan request, session, cookies, dsb.\n",
    "\n",
    "Konfigurasi LocaleResolver menggunakan session adalah sebagai berikut:\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "@Bean\n",
    "public SessionLocaleResolver localeResolver() {\n",
    "    SessionLocaleResolver slr = new SessionLocaleResolver();\n",
    "    slr.setDefaultLocale(Locale.US);\n",
    "    return slr;\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 2. LocaleChangeInterceptor\n",
    "\n",
    "Bertujuan untuk mengubah locale yang sedang digunakan menjadi locale lain yang diinginkan menggunakan parameter tertentu pada URL, misal ```\\index?lang=id```.\n",
    "\n",
    "Konfigurasi LocaleChangeInterceptor adalah sebagai berikut:\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "@Bean\n",
    "public LocaleChangeInterceptor localeChangeInterceptor() {\n",
    "    LocaleChangeInterceptor lci = new LocaleChangeInterceptor();\n",
    "    lci.setParamName(\"lang\");\n",
    "    return lci;\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Agar LocaleChangeInterceptor berfungsi, ```@Bean``` tersebut ditambahkan ke dalam registry interceptor aplikasi.\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "@Override\n",
    "public void addInterceptors(InterceptorRegistry registry) {\n",
    "    registry.addInterceptor(localeChangeInterceptor());\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 3. MessageSource\n",
    "\n",
    "Secara default, file locale terletak pada **src/main/resources** dengan nama file ```messages.properties``` dan ```messages_xx.properties``` dimana ```xx``` menunjukkan kode locale tertentu. Namun, apabila ingin dimasukkan ke dalam folder tertentu (misal: **src/main/resources/i18n**), maka perlu adanya konfigurasi sebagai berikut:\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "@Bean\n",
    "public MessageSource messageSource() {\n",
    "    ReloadableResourceBundleMessageSource messageSource = new ReloadableResourceBundleMessageSource();\n",
    "    messageSource.setBasename(\"classpath:/i18n/messages\");\n",
    "    messageSource.setDefaultEncoding(\"UTF-8\");\n",
    "    return messageSource;\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Semua konfigurasi tersebut di atas dituliskan pada ```AppConfig.java```.\n",
    "\n",
    "### HTML Page\n",
    "\n",
    "Pada halaman html, semua text diganti dengan **key** yang bersesuaian yang ada pada file locale. \n",
    "\n",
    "```html\n",
    "<a href=\"addStudent\" th:utext=\"#{lang.addstudent}\"></a>\n",
    "<table border=\"1\">\n",
    "    <tr>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.username}\"></td>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.firstname}\"></td>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.lastname}\"></td>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.email}\"></td>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.gender}\"></td>\n",
    "        <td th:utext=\"#{lang.country}\"></td>\n",
    "    </tr>\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "## Repository\n",
    "\n",
    "File pada package Repository bertujuan untuk menyimpan method-method terkait transaksi data pada setiap model agar lebih rapi dan sistematis.\n",
    "\n",
    "Contoh dari ```CountryRepository.java``` yang bertujuan untuk menyimpan key dan value country pada model Country.\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "@Repository\n",
    "public class CountryRepository {\n",
    "\tprivate static final Map<String, Country> COUNTRIES=new HashMap<String, Country>();\n",
    "\t\n",
    "\tstatic {\n",
    "\t\tCountry id  = new Country(\"ID\",\"Indonesia\");\n",
    "\t\tCountry uk  = new Country(\"UK\",\"United Kingdom\");\n",
    "\t\tCountry us  = new Country(\"US\",\"United States\");\n",
    "\t\tCountry au  = new Country(\"AU\",\"Australia\");\n",
    "\t\t\n",
    "\t\tCOUNTRIES.put(id.getKey(),id);\n",
    "\t\tCOUNTRIES.put(uk.getKey(),uk);\n",
    "\t\tCOUNTRIES.put(us.getKey(),us);\n",
    "\t\tCOUNTRIES.put(au.getKey(),au);\n",
    "\t}\n",
    "\t\n",
    "\tpublic List<Country> listAllCountries(){\n",
    "\t\tList<Country> countries = new  ArrayList<Country>();\n",
    "\t\tcountries.addAll(COUNTRIES.values());\n",
    "\t\treturn countries;\n",
    "\t}\n",
    "\n",
    "\tpublic Map<String, Country> mapCountries(){\n",
    "\t\treturn COUNTRIES;\n",
    "\t}\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "## Custom Validator\n",
    "\n",
    "Berfungsi untuk membuat validasi pada isian-isian form secara custom. Agar rapi dan sistematis, custom validator disimpan pada package Validator pada file class validator tertentu dalam hal ini ```StudentValidator.java```.\n",
    "\n",
    "Ada beberapa validasi yang dibuat dan disimpan pada method ```validate``` di dalam ```StudentValidator.java```, di antaranya:\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. Isian ```field``` tidak boleh kosong\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "Student student = (Student) target;\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"userName\", \"NotEmpty.student.username\");\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"firstName\", \"NotEmpty.student.firstname\");\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"lastName\", \"NotEmpty.student.lastname\");\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"email\", \"NotEmpty.student.email\");\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"gender\", \"NotEmpty.student.gender\");\n",
    "ValidationUtils.rejectIfEmpty(errors, \"country\", \"NotEmpty.student.country\");\n",
    "```\n",
    "### 2. Cek duplicate ```username``` dan ```email```\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "// Check duplicate username\n",
    "if(studentRepository.findStudentUserName(student.getUserName())!=null) {\n",
    "    errors.rejectValue(\"userName\", \"Duplicate.student.username\");\n",
    "}\n",
    "//check duplicate email\n",
    "if(studentRepository.findStudentUserName(student.getEmail())!=null) {\n",
    "    errors.rejectValue(\"email\", \"Duplicate.student.email\");\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Method pada ```StudentRepository.java```\n",
    "\n",
    "```java\n",
    "public Student findStudentUserName(String username) {\n",
    "    Collection<Student> students = STUDENTS.values();\n",
    "    for(Student s: students) {\n",
    "        if(s.getUserName().equals(username)) {\n",
    "            return s;\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    return null;\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "public Student findEmail(String email) {\n",
    "    Collection<Student> students = STUDENTS.values();\n",
    "    for(Student s: students) {\n",
    "        if(s.getEmail().equals(email)) {\n",
    "            return s;\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    return null;\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
